data.sunServiceSchema:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<ServicesConfiguration><Service name="RadiusServerService" version="1.0"><Schema i18nFileName="radiusServer"  i18nKey="radius-server-service-description"  revisionNumber="1"  serviceHierarchy="/DSAMEConfig/RadiusServerService" >

            <Global hideConfigUI="no"  validate="yes" >
                <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="a-radius-listener-enabled-label"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="radiusListenerEnabled"  order="200"  syntax="string"  type="single_choice" >
                    <ChoiceValues>
                        <ChoiceValue i18nKey="choiceYES" >YES</ChoiceValue>
                        <ChoiceValue i18nKey="choiceNO" >NO</ChoiceValue>
                    </ChoiceValues>
                    <DefaultValues>
                        <Value>NO</Value>
                    </DefaultValues>
                </AttributeSchema>

                <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="b-radius-port"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="radiusServerPort"  order="400"  rangeEnd="65535"  rangeStart="1025"  syntax="number_range"  type="single" >
                    <DefaultValues>
                        <Value>1812</Value>
                    </DefaultValues>
                </AttributeSchema>

                <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="c-radius-thread-pool-core-size"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="radiusThreadPoolCoreSize"  order="600"  rangeEnd="100"  rangeStart="1"  syntax="number_range"  type="single" >
                    <DefaultValues>
                        <Value>1</Value>
                    </DefaultValues>
                </AttributeSchema>

                <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="d-radius-thread-pool-max-size"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="radiusThreadPoolMaxSize"  order="800"  rangeEnd="100"  rangeStart="1"  syntax="number_range"  type="single" >
                    <DefaultValues>
                        <Value>10</Value>
                    </DefaultValues>
                </AttributeSchema>

                <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="e-radius-thread-pool-keepalive-seconds"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="radiusThreadPoolKeepaliveSeconds"  order="1000"  rangeEnd="3600"  rangeStart="1"  syntax="number_range"  type="single" >
                    <DefaultValues>
                        <Value>10</Value>
                    </DefaultValues>
                </AttributeSchema>

                <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="f-radius-thread-pool-queue-size"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="radiusThreadPoolQueueSize"  order="1100"  rangeEnd="1000"  rangeStart="1"  syntax="number_range"  type="single" >
                    <DefaultValues>
                        <Value>20</Value>
                    </DefaultValues>
                </AttributeSchema>

                <SubSchema hideConfigUI="no"  i18nFileName="radiusServer"  i18nKey="client-config-instance"  inheritance="multiple"  maintainPriority="no"  name="radiusClient"  realmCloneable="yes"  supportsApplicableOrganization="no"  validate="yes" >
                    <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="a-client-ip-address-label"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="clientIpAddress"  order="100"  syntax="string"  type="single" >
                         <DefaultValues>
                            <Value>/127.0.0.1</Value>
                        </DefaultValues>                                    
                    </AttributeSchema>
                        
                    <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="b-client-secret-label"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="clientSecret"  order="300"  syntax="string"  type="single" >
                        <DefaultValues>
                            <DefaultValuesClassName className="org.forgerock.openam.radius.server.config.DefaultClientSecretGenerator" >
                            </DefaultValuesClassName>
                        </DefaultValues>
                    </AttributeSchema>
                    
                    <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="c-client-log-packets"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="clientPacketsLogged"  order="500"  syntax="string"  type="single_choice" >
                        <ChoiceValues>
                            <ChoiceValue i18nKey="choiceYES" >YES</ChoiceValue>
                            <ChoiceValue i18nKey="choiceNO" >NO</ChoiceValue>
                        </ChoiceValues>
                        <DefaultValues>
                            <Value>NO</Value>
                        </DefaultValues>
                    </AttributeSchema>

                    <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="d-handler-class"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="handlerClass"  order="700"  syntax="string"  type="single" >
                        <DefaultValues>
                            <Value>org.forgerock.openam.radius.server.spi.handlers.OpenAMAuthHandler</Value>
                        </DefaultValues>

                    </AttributeSchema>
                    <AttributeSchema cosQualifier="default"  hideConfigUI="no"  i18nKey="e-handler-config-params"  isSearchable="no"  listOrder="natural"  name="handlerConfig"  order="900"  syntax="string"  type="list" >
                        <DefaultValues>
                            <Value>realm=/</Value>
                            <Value>chain=ldapService</Value>
                        </DefaultValues>
                    </AttributeSchema>

                </SubSchema>
            </Global>
            
            <Organization hideConfigUI="no" >
            </Organization>

        </Schema></Service></ServicesConfiguration>
